Class OrderBook

  • java.lang.Object
    • OrderBook

  • public class OrderBook
extends java.lang.Object
    OrderBook class This class stores the list of all the orders which have been placed during the day. Note:- Only the orders placed during the current session will be available from this class. Orders placed before the connection was made will not be available via this class.
